{"tid":1383940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句到尾  魚肉腸同香蕉推上前線先","createTime":"2019-07-29T20:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T23:26:02.000Z","uid":196615,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eb7104852e4eb0337a6fc69b3e3cf0362d58746f","tid":1383940,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uACYk13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuACYk13.jpg&h=0468d8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/azWBR8J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FazWBR8J.jpg&h=92553912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/msJgR9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmsJgR9N.jpg&h=c97877e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知魚肉腸好多防腐劑<br />\n我知好多仔女好想有飯落肚好想食到華御結<br />\n但係行軍打仗糧草就係要便攜同回血快<br />\n<br />\n最重要係－－－平時周街買到入定大貨唔洗等地鐵舖頭仔返貨呀！<br />\n<br />\n推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3222834a88916f02cde2d580094f2ecac6bd81","tid":1383940,"uid":114186,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:24:16.000Z","msg":"香蕉一物二用 正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254d38b926f78b44ce515a173710b0261cb816d4","tid":1383940,"uid":196615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:24:24.000Z","msg":"同埋唔係叫你買完擺低就散呀<br />\n<br />\n你同我拎上前線逐個問逐個派呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0031c956db2d12baef431ce13ea19ed357f745","tid":1383940,"uid":196615,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:27:03.000Z","msg":"自推童年回憶魚肉腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話晒都係肉起碼好過麵包乾餅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57e7ad95abb7fedf7b4d5475e83b7a07f2c232c","tid":1383940,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:33:29.000Z","msg":"夜媽媽無人惟有自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee21d6501c3983dd8fb430d1fd213baf61224f90","tid":1383940,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:35:26.000Z","msg":"魚肉腸好好食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa4526fd17663da610b254ecf46a8373203936c","tid":1383940,"uid":196615,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee21d6501c3983dd8fb430d1fd213baf61224f90","tid":1383940,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:35:26.000Z","msg":"魚肉腸好好食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:42:05.000Z","msg":"好好食要繼續推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c168175315bb8174ff0cf3149f8087b18d9820c","tid":1383940,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"beb75d397f8bd3e8e